You had a compile error here independent of the new feature: captureAndStore referenced primaryLocatorStr, a variable that was never declared (the parameter is named primaryLocator). The fix was to use the primaryLocator parameter consistently — both as the third argument to buildSmartLocatorBundle and as the primaryLocator field in saveElement. That value originates at the call sites as finalLocator.toString().
